  "modelText": ["DESCRIPTION:\n; Dose in mg\n; Time in hours\n\n[LONGITUDINAL]\ninput = {ka, Vd, CL}\n\nPK:\ncompartment(cmt = 1, amount = Ad)\niv(cmt = 1, adm = 1)\n\nEQUATION:\n;;; Explicit functions\nCc = Ac/Vd  \t\t\t\t\t\t; mg/L\n\n;;; Initial conditions\nAd_0 = 0  \t\t\t; mg\nAc_0 = 0  \t\t\t; mg\n\n;;; ODEs\nddt_Ad = - ka*Ad \nddt_Ac = ka*Ad - CL*Cc\n\nOUTPUT:\noutput = {Cc}"]
